      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">What Happens When the Maestro Quits?</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">Your best agent operator built the coordination layer that makes your AI team work. They documented nothing structured. They just gave two weeks notice. Everything they learned is about to walk out the door.</p>
